    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this protocol is to advertise, recruit, and do a preliminary screen for
      various clinical trials. Information collected will be entered in a database available to
      researchers connected with the Stanford/VA Aging Clinical Research Center, located at VA
      Palo Alto Health Care System, Palo Alto Division.
    </textblock>
